 --></p></div><div class="text-sm"><h4 class="font-bold"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Additional Ability: Contractual Agreement<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class="text-sm zzz-fmt"><!-- -->When another character in your squad shares the same Attribute or Faction:<br/>While the Shield from <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Core Passive: Guardian</span> is in effect, the character's CRIT Rate is increased by 16%.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div><!--]--><!-- --></div>`],coreGrowthStat:{12101:25,30501:1200}}},1131:{name:"SOUKAKU",camp:"6",rarity:"3",weaponType:"4",ElementType:"202",hitType:["101"],id:"1131",growthStat:{11101:{base:645,growth:875424,asc:443},12101:{base:96,growth:54915,asc:34},13101:{base:48,growth:65085,asc:33}},staticStats:{12201:86,20101:5e4,21101:5e5,23101:0,30501:12e3,31201:96,31401:93},skillKit:{0:{skillId:0,desc:['<div class="text-sm"><h4 class="font-bold"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Making Rice Cakes<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class="text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt"><!-- -->Press <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to 3 attacks, dealing <span style="color: #F0D12B">Physical DMG</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>','<span class="text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt"><!-- -->Press <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to 3 attacks, dealing <span style="color: #F0D12B">Physical DMG</span>.<!-- --></span>','<div class="text-sm"><h4 class="font-bold"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Making Rice Cakes (Frosted Banner)<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class="text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt"><!-- -->When <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Frosted Banner</span> is active, press <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to 3 faster attacks in front, dealing <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>','<span class="text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt"><!-- -->When <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Frosted Banner</span> is active, press <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to 3 faster attacks in front, dealing <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>.<!-- --></span>'],subSkills:{"BASIC ATTACK: MAKING RICE CAKES":{"1st-Hit":{hitID:["1131001"],dmg:{base:662e3,growth:61e3},daze:{base:331e3,growth:16e3},formula:"{1131001}"},"2nd-Hit":{hitID:["1131002"],dmg:{base:2163e3,growth:197e3},daze:{base:188e4,growth:86e3},formula:"{1131002}"},"3rd-Hit":{hitID:["1131003"],dmg:{base:2931e3,growth:267e3},daze:{base:2217e3,growth:101e3},formula:"{1131003}"}},"BASIC ATTACK: MAKING RICE CAKES (FROSTED BANNER)":{"1st-Hit":{hitID:["1131004"],dmg:{base:766e3,growth:7e4},daze:{base:466e3,growth:22e3},formula:"{1131004}"},"2nd-Hit":{hitID:["1131005"],dmg:{base:2285e3,growth:208e3},daze:{base:1275e3,growth:58e3},formula:"{1131005}"},"3rd-Hit":{hitID:["1131006"],dmg:{base:5114e3,growth:465e3},daze:{base:2633e3,growth:12e4},formula:"{1131006}"}}}},1:{skillId:1,desc:['<div class="text-sm"><h4 class="font-bold"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Cooling Bento<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class="text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt"><!-- -->Press <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp"/> to activate:<br/>Soukaku releases a wind current in front of her and unleashes her finishing move, dealing <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>During skill activation, Anti-Interrupt level increases, and DMG taken is reduced by 40%.<br/>Holding <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp"/> while using this skill allows for a quick transition to <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>','<span class="text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt"><!-- -->Press <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp"/> to activate:<br/>Soukaku releases a wind current in front of her and unleashes her finishing move, dealing <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>During skill activation, Anti-Interrupt level increases, and DMG taken is reduced by 40%.<br/>Holding <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp"/> while using this skill allows for a quick transition to <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span>.<!-- --></span>',`<div class="text-sm"><h4 class="font-bold"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Fanning Mosquitoes<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class="text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp"/> to activate:<br/>Releases wind currents of extended range in front of her, dealing massive <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>This skill can be triggered consecutively by pressing repeatedly. Each use consumes a specified amount of Energy. When Soukaku's Energy is depleted, or you stop pressing the button, she unleashes a powerful finishing move that deals massive <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>During skill activation, Anti-Interrupt level increases, and DMG taken is reduced by 40%.<br/>Holding <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp"/> while using this skill allows for a quick transition to <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>`,`<span class="text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp"/> to activate:<br/>Releases wind currents of extended range in front of her, dealing massive <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>This skill can be triggered consecutively by pressing repeatedly. Each use consumes a specified amount of Energy. When Soukaku's Energy is depleted, or you stop pressing the button, she unleashes a powerful finishing move that deals massive <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>During skill activation, Anti-Interrupt level increases, and DMG taken is reduced by 40%.<br/>Holding <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp"/> while using this skill allows for a quick transition to <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span>.<!-- --></span>`,`<div class="text-sm"><h4 class="font-bold"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Rally!<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class="text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt"><!-- -->Hold <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp"/> to activate:<br/>Soukaku plunges her weapon into the ground, morphs it into a flag, and launches <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span>, dealing <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>. Hitting an enemy with <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span> triggers a <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Quick Assist</span>.<br/>Pressing <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp"/> or <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp"/> after <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span> activates a Special Attack as she retracts the flag, dealing <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>If Soukaku owns 3 stacks of <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortex</span> on using <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span>, she consumes all 3 stacks and enters the <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Frosted Banner</span> state. In the <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Frosted Banner</span> state, she can unleash an enhanced <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Basic Attack</span> or an enhanced <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Dash Attack</span>, dealing massive <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>. This effect can last up to 45s or stack up to 6 times.<br/>Soukaku's weapon gains <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortexes</span> in the following circumstances:<br/>Gains 1 stack of <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortex</span> when launching an <span style="color: #FFFFFF">EX Special Attack</span>,<br/>Gains 1 stack of <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortex</span> when launching a <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Chain Attack</span>,<br/>Gains 3 stacks of <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortex</span> when launching an <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Ultimate</span>.<br/>Soukaku can accumulate a maximum of 3 stacks of <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortex</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>`,`<span class="text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt"><!-- -->Hold <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp"/> to activate:<br/>Soukaku plunges her weapon into the ground, morphs it into a flag, and launches <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span>, dealing <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>. Hitting an enemy with <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span> triggers a <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Quick Assist</span>.<br/>Pressing <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp"/> or <img alt="" class="h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon" src="https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp"/> after <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span> activates a Special Attack as she retracts the flag, dealing <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>If Soukaku owns 3 stacks of <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortex</span> on using <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Fly the Flag</span>, she consumes all 3 stacks and enters the <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Frosted Banner</span> state. In the <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Frosted Banner</span> state, she can unleash an enhanced <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Basic Attack</span> or an enhanced <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Dash Attack</span>, dealing massive <span style="color: #98EFF0">Ice DMG</span>. This effect can last up to 45s or stack up to 6 times.<br/>Soukaku's weapon gains <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortexes</span> in the following circumstances:<br/>Gains 1 stack of <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortex</span> when launching an <span style="color: #FFFFFF">EX Special Attack</span>,<br/>Gains 1 stack of <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortex</span> when launching a <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Chain Attack</span>,<br/>Gains 3 stacks of <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortex</span> when launching an <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Ultimate</span>.<br/>Soukaku can accumulate a maximum of 3 stacks of <span style="color: #FFFFFF">Vortex</span>.<!-- --></span>`],subSkills:{"SPECIAL ATTACK: COOLING BENTO":{"1st-Hit":{hitID:["1131008"],dmg:{base:284e3,growth:26e3},daze:{base:284e3,growth:13e3},formula:"{1131008}"},"Finishing Move":{hitID:["1131009"],dmg:{base:1001e3,growth:91e3},daze:{base:1001e3,growth:46e3},formula:"{1131009}"}},"EX SPECIAL AT